                  </hi>. I have a pair of boots pawned with me by a man, but I have no recollection of the person.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18441021-name-600" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18441021-name-600" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
